# CODEOWNERS — who must review changes to which areas.
#
# When "Require review from Code Owners" is enabled on the branch ruleset, a PR
# touching a matched path cannot merge until a listed owner approves. Owners
# must have write access to the repo. Last matching pattern wins, so keep the
# specific rules below the general one.
#
# As the project grows, replace @zkWizard with team handles (e.g. @org/rendering)
# and uncomment the area-based rules so review routes to domain experts.

# Default owner for everything in the repo.
*                       @zkWizard

# --- Area ownership (uncomment & assign as maintainers come on board) ---------
# Rendering / Three.js scene
# /src/main.ts           @zkWizard
# *.glsl                 @zkWizard

# Geo / coordinate math & data pipeline
# /src/lib/              @zkWizard

# Build, CI, and security-sensitive config
# /.github/              @zkWizard
# /vite.config.ts        @zkWizard
# /tsconfig.json         @zkWizard
# /eslint.config.js      @zkWizard
